类 StackTraceSampleCoordinator.PendingStackTraceSample

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.rest.handler.legacy.backpressure.StackTraceSampleCoordinator.PendingStackTraceSample
  • 封闭类:
    StackTraceSampleCoordinator

    private static class StackTraceSampleCoordinator.PendingStackTraceSample
extends java.lang.Object
    A pending stack trace sample, which collects stack traces and owns a StackTraceSample promise.

    Access pending sample in lock scope.
